SUMMARY:Judaism Decoded
DESCRIPTION:Judaism Decoded sheds light on the mysteries surrounding biblical interpretation. How do we know our interpretation is true? If it is true\, why is it subject to differences of opinion? And with so many interpretations to choose from\, how do we know which one reflects its original intent? \nDiscover the sheer elegance of the “source code” on which Torah law is built; enjoy the razor-sharp reasoning\, intelligent debate\, and compelling arguments of the Talmudic dialectic; and get a fascinating\, behind-the-scenes glimpse of the most intellectually sophisticated religion in existence.
URL:https://jewishfed.org/event/judaism-decoded/2026-03-03/
LOCATION:Chabad Jewish Center of Petaluma\, 3921 Fabian Way\, Petaluma\, CA\, 94303
CATEGORIES:Community Event
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://jewishfed.org/wp-content/uploads/Screenshot-2025-10-23-160146.png
