SUMMARY:The Art of Havruta: A Mishnah Study Series with Hadar
DESCRIPTION:Rabbi David Kasher will offer brief teachings on the philosophy of havruta study and guide us through the themes and structure of the Mishnah chapters from Hadar’s Project Zug Course “The Mishnah In Context”. This is an opportunity to get to know a core genre of Jewish text while developing the skills and spirit of classical havruta learning. \nTue\, Feb 24\, 6:30 – 8:30 PM at Congregation Emanu El (2 Lake St\, San Francisco\, CA 94118)\nTue\, Mar 24\, 6:30 – 8:30 PM at Congregation Beth Sholom (301 14th Ave\, San Francisco\, CA 94118)
