SUMMARY:Beth Sholom Annual Gala — L’dor V’dor: Stories We Carry Forward
DESCRIPTION:Join us for our annual fundraiser with dinner and dancing in celebration of the stories we carry forward — the memories\, traditions\, and moments that connect us across generations. L’dor V’dor isn’t just about honoring our history; it’s about weaving together the diverse journeys that make CBS the vibrant community it is today. Whether you’ve been part of our congregation for decades or joined us recently\, this is an evening to celebrate the connections that bind us together and the joy of being part of something larger than ourselves.
URL:https://jewishfed.org/event/beth-sholom-annual-gala-ldor-vdor-stories-we-carry-forward/
