SUMMARY:Creekside Connections with Congregation Rodef Sholom
DESCRIPTION:Whether you’re a long-time local or new to the neighborhood\, join us at Creek Park in downtown San Anselmo to celebrate the simple joy of a Saturday evening connecting with community. Grab some dinner from neighboring restaurants\, bring a blanket or comfy chair\, and settle in for some live music and easy schmoozing. We’ll wrap up our time together with havdalah—a short\, melodic ritual to help us unplug from the week behind us and transition to the one ahead. Come exactly as you are; we can’t wait to welcome you!
