SUMMARY:Camp Aleph | Summer 2026
DESCRIPTION:Aleph is for Awesome. Aleph is for Amazing. Aleph is for #1. \nWe are delighted that you are joining us\, and we are certain that your children will have a wonderful camp experience. The counselors and staff at Camp Aleph are eager to greet your children with many fun and exciting programs planned for this year. \n\nCamp Aleph offers a 2-week summer program for children ages 4 through 13.\nCamp Aleph for girls ages 13-14.\nCamp Aleph Adventures program for boys ages 11-13.\n\nWe are looking forward to an amazing summer!
URL:https://jewishfed.org/event/camp-aleph-summer-2026/
